 = \int^l_0 ( x(s)y_s(s) - \overline{y}(s)x_s(s)) \,ds \le \int^l_0 \sqrt{ (x(s)y_s(s) - \overline{y}(s)x_s(s))^2} \,ds \stackrel{*}{\le}
 \stackrel{*}{\le} \int^l_0 \sqrt{ (x^2(s) + \overline{y}^2(s))} \,ds = lr
